<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="nice-adj">nice <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /naɪs/    美 /naɪs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>美好的；极好的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What <strong>a nice day</strong>, isn’t it?
天气真好，对吧？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You did a good job today. <strong>Nice work</strong>, James! 
你今天干得不错。好样的，詹姆斯！</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>宜人的；愉快的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a nice hot bath 
舒服的热水澡</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>have a <strong>nice time</strong> 
玩得开心</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>亲切的；友好的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>be <strong>nice to sb</strong>
对某人友善</p></div>

<ul>
<li>it is nice of sb to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is nice of you to help me. 
你真好，帮了我的忙。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>nicely /'naɪsli/ adv   </p></div>